; DNS zone for family-testing.com -> Render
; Import into GoDaddy AFTER deleting conflicting records (see CUSTOM_DOMAIN_GODADDY.md)

$TTL 600
$ORIGIN family-testing.com.

; Root domain -> Render load balancer
@       IN      A       216.24.57.1

; www -> Render service
www     IN      CNAME   family-testing-services.onrender.com.
